'''Musician droids''' were [[Droid/Legends|droids]] programmed and equipped to play [[Music/Legends|music]]. They were very common in [[Cantina/Legends|cantinas]], bars and dance halls. The [[Tashelin serenading droid]] was a type of music droid.<ref name="TOR">''[[Star Wars: The Old Republic]]''</ref>

